section.section:
The notice required under paragraph (1) of this subsection shall contain:
The name of the trust;
The name of the person who created the trust;
The date on which the trust was established;
The name and address of the corporate fiduciary trustee seeking to terminate the trust;
The name of any cotrustee;
A statement that the effective date of the termination shall be at least 90 days after the date on which notice under paragraph (1) of this subsection has been received by each cotrustee and each beneficiary;
A statement of the reasons for termination of the trust;
The approximate amount and the manner of calculation of each distribution of the trust estate; and
A statement of the right to object and the procedures to follow under subsection (d) of this section.
